<div class="card">
    <div class="card-header border-bottom">
        <h4 class="card-title">Change Password</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body pt-1">
        <!-- form -->
        <form class="validate-form" id="security-form">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 mb-1">
                    <label class="form-label" for="oldPassword">현재 비밀번호</label>
                    <div class="input-group form-password-toggle input-group-merge">
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="oldPassword" name="oldPassword" placeholder="현재 비밀 번호를 입력해 주세요" />
                        <div class="input-group-text cursor-pointer">
                            <i data-feather="eye"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 mb-1">
                    <label class="form-label" for="newPassword">New Password</label>
                    <div class="input-group form-password-toggle input-group-merge">
                        <input type="password" id="newPassword" name="newPassword" class="form-control" placeholder="새로운 비밀번호를 입력해 주세요" />
                        <div class="input-group-text cursor-pointer">
                            <i data-feather="eye"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 mb-1">
                    <label class="form-label" for="reNewPassword">Retype New Password</label>
                    <div class="input-group form-password-toggle input-group-merge">
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="reNewPassword" name="reNewPassword" placeholder="비밀번호를 다시 입력해 주세요" />
                        <div class="input-group-text cursor-pointer"><i data-feather="eye"></i></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12">
                    <p class="fw-bolder">Password requirements:</p>
                    <ul class="ps-1 ms-25">
                        <li class="mb-50">단순한 비밀번호를 설정하시면 크롬 브라우저에서 비밀번호 유출되었다는 팝업이 나올수 있습니다.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary me-1 mt-1 waves-effect waves-float waves-light">Save changes</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>

    </div>
</div>